aham.hannah/eq/resources/niffo60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Adventures</span><hr size=1> Hi Ho,<br><br>Just thought I would share with you last nights gaming fun:<br><br>It all began as 3 young Barbarians (Torson, Kilcie and Blukrystal) set off from the Qeynos Hills with the goal of meeting some far distant allies who were battling with Clan Crushbone. This journey would comprise some 13 zones by the time we were bound at the famous Orc Lift. There we met the tiny little Mattila, Lilta and then Chantus.<br>Together we merry band assualted Crushbone and had a fun time indeed slaying and being slain. It was almost like a planned raid in the end - if only we all had Victus Fortis after our name  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>Anyhow, we all had a blast and there were a few others popping in to join the fun at various points.<br><br>Cant wait until next friday now.....<br><br>Kiclie and the Niffo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uwarninwraithlore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Warnin Wraithlore</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.telusplanet.net/public/canadak/sig.JPG BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 220<br> <font color=#8B4513>(2/16/01 5:12:24 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.telusplanet.net/public/canadak/warnin1.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Adventures</span><hr size=1> I knew I shoulda logged on last night!  Was perched upon me couch watching TV with the beast some call Wife.  Rave coulda joined the fun maybe.  And I hear from Raloth we could have been official. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br>Glad to see many Crushbone Orcs fell to our brave and stoid friends.<br><br>battle on,<br>-Warnin <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ugumbrils.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gumbrils</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#8B4513>(2/17/01 4:05:44 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/gumbrils60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Adventures</span><hr size=1> Yes it was great fun, lots of orcs being mushed, and a few PCs being mushed. It was good to see all those hulking ba-bas who couldn't fit through the doors in Kelethin. Most amusing.<br><br>It was also amusing hearing Chantus pulling her hair out each time someone attacked the orc she'd just mezzed.<br><br>Lilta logged in last night as well and teamed up with Kilcie for a bit (noticed a Lunitune corpse lying around in Crush as well) which was cool. Unfortunately people kept training Dvinn and emissaries etc, which led to many rather bloody deaths :(.<br><br>Gumbrils (on behalf of Lilta) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ulittleniffo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LittleNiffo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#8B4513>(2/18/01 2:12:06 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/niffo60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Adventures</span><hr size=1> Hi Ho,<br><br>yesindeed:<br>Kilcie in battle with friends in clearing out from zone with friends.<br>Nice Red Lego and everything.<br>XYZ Shouts TRAIN<br>XYZ Shouts Dvinn to Zone<br>Kilcie says hmmm that could be fun.<br>battle continues (lego looking beaten)<br>Kilcies health bar takes a sudden beating<br>Dvinn spills Kilcies blood all over the place<br>Dvinn then flays a few others into small pieces.<br><br>one day soon...<br><br>Kilcie backstabs Dvinn for 40<br>You have killed Dvinn    YAY<br><br>Battle Assassin from the North,<br>Kilcie <p><font color="#FF3333">Feet be well,<br>Niffo.</font> </p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/utaallon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taallon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#8B4513>(2/20/01 10:44:07 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/taallon60x60.jpg  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Adventures</span><hr size=1> Gippen and I were at the Sarnak castle on Sunday night.  We had a very successful grp going.  After a very long battle, gippen had left so we had no healer and most of our grp was tattered and torn someone trained 4 sarnaks on us.<br><br>Our very large tank was being killed, another druid took off like lightening since he was in wolf form and it was just me and the tank and I was low on mana.  I decided to cast an AoE spell and train the sarnaks away from the grp since we were going to die.<br><br>I was running like mad and getting wacked pretty good (while all this was going on I was in communication with Ronstad telling him where grp was and that he could join).  Well ronstad happened to be at the entrance of the sarnak castle just as this slow ass elf rounded the corner.  I was almost dead when Ronstad casted LoH on me and saved my life, but to my demise I could not save Ronstads.<br><br>He saved my life only to sacrifice his own.  Ronstad truely is an individual that holds honor and valor close to his heart and who I will repay some day.  Thanks<br><br>Taallon Veneficus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ulittleniffo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LittleNiffo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 129<br> <font color=#8B4513>(2/24/01 2:02:09 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/niffo60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Adventures</span><hr size=1> Hi Ho,<br><br>Brave work indeed little Rony<br>Sounds like a scary zone to have a group fade away in... <p><font color="#FF3333">Feet be well,<br>Niffo.</font> </p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.showMessage?topicID=41.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.showMessage?topicID=46.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=59.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.threadControl?topicID=59.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=59.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm23.unsubscribeUnr